summary: An ordinance granting to Frederick and Nelson Company, a corporation, its successors and assigns, a franchise to construct, maintain and operate a bridge across and over alley in block 12, Boren & Denny's Addition to the City of Seattle for the purpose of connecting the building situated on lots 2, 3, 6 and 7, with the building situated on lot 1 of said block 12 of said addition.
